A classic design for training and competition with a women’s specific fit. Made from our exclusive microfiber CS Tech fabric for superior wicking and moisture management the performance run top can be fully printed with your designs and logos. 


Features:



  • Constructed of CS Tech fabric.

  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+.

  • No annoying label tags at the neck

  • Fully customisable. 

  •  Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more.


Women's Performance Run Top available in V-neck only.

Part of our exclusive Women’s specific collection – Donna Forte. Our Donna Forte full length run tight is perfect for all activities, featuring an Italian made pre dyed black lycra offering premium comfort and fit. A true all purpose garment.



- NOTE – This item cannot be customized.


- Elasticised 1.5 inch waistband for optimal comfort.


- Features a mix of double needle cover stitch and exposed flatlock stitching to provide the best in comfort and premium look and feel.

column1: Apex Women's Run Top (V Neck Design)
column4:
The Champion System Apex Run Top is constructed of our exclusive Champion System  CS AirLite fabric with strategically placed mesh side panels for even greater breathability and flatlock seams for increased comfort. A must for training and competition.


Features:



  • Constructed of CS AirLite fabric.

  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+.

  • No annoying label tags at the neck

  • Fully customisable. 

  • Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more.

Part of our exclusive Women’s specific collection – Donna Forte. Our Donna Forte run short is designed specifically for females who run, race or train.

- Elasticised 2.5 inch waistband with drawstring for optimal comfort – waistband cannot be printed and will come in black only


- CS Windguard fabric construction for body of shorts fully printable


- Split sides for increased range of movement


- Woman’s specific cut


- Small open key/coin pocket in front of waistband


- Larger zippered pocket in rear of waistband for key/ipod storage


- Fully lined inside

Racerback design made with lightweight moisture wicking fabric make this performance singlet ideal for training and competition. Made from our exclusive CS Tech Lite fabric, the Bella Racerback Singlet can be fully printed with your designs and logos.



- Fully Customisable


- CS Tech Lite fabric


- Lightweight and moisture wicking


- Tagless


- Great for running, hiking, yoga, and more.

Part of our new Donna Forte Women’s Specific range designed specifically for women. The Donna Forte compact tight is a premium tight short designed to be worn by itself or under another garment. Offering high levels of compression and comfort the Donna Forte Compact tight is an all round performer whether running, in the gym, practicing yoga or relaxing at the coffee shop.



- Made for our CS Contour, Italian made premium pre-dyed black lycra


- Available in standard and LONG length options


- Exposed flat lock stitch construction enabling a close fit and excellent comfort


- Separate crotch panel to reduce chaffing and improve comfort


- 1.5 inch elasticated waist band


- NOTE: This garment can not be customised
